# Custom CSS üé®

Create your own efficiently.

```javascript
function spin(node, { duration }) {
  return {
    duration,
    css: t => {
      const eased = elasticOut(t);
      return `transform: scale(${eased}) rotate(${eased * 1080}deg)`;
    }
  };
}
```
